# SHA-256 Release Manifest

This file will contain SHA-256 hashes for release v0.3.1 artifacts.

Current status: pending final hash generation.

Expected format:

<sha256_hash>  README.md
<sha256_hash>  technical-note-v0.3.1.md
<sha256_hash>  references.md
<sha256_hash>  solver/<file>
<sha256_hash>  examples/<file>

Purpose:
This manifest allows independent auditors to verify that the published artifacts have not been modified after release.

Scope limitation:
A SHA-256 manifest proves integrity of the listed artifacts after hashing.
It does not prove the truth or correctness of the original content.
